## Quick Reference

### Setup Checklist
- [ ] Install Firebase SDK
- [ ] Configure environment variables
- [ ] Enable offline persistence
- [ ] Use UUID-based document IDs

### Data Structure Rules
- **Collections**: Top-level for independent entities
- **Subcollections**: For nested, parent-owned data
- **Nesting limit**: Max 3 levels deep
- **Document structure**: Flat, not deeply nested

### Offline Patterns
- **UUIDs**: Client-generated IDs (v4)
- **Persistence**: Enable IndexedDB (web) or default (RN)
- **Cache size**: Configure as needed (default 40MB)
- **Conflict resolution**: Last write wins (see @46-firebase-repository.mdc)

